Webex App | Send a message
In Webex App, messages are where you chat with colleagues, and share content and ideas. You can send a message to someone directly or to a group space.
Desktop
iOS
Android
Web
1
Go to Messaging , select a person or a space from your spaces list.
2
Click the message area and then type your message.
You can include files or add personality with emojis or animated GIFs, and also add formatting or Markdown to make your messages stand out or be easier to read.
3
Click or press Enter, to send your message.